(9, 4, 33, 'Adizero Boston 12 Shoes', 'Adidas', 22000, 25000, '<pre style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 32px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space-collapse: preserve-breaks;\"><font style=\"\" face=\"arial\" size=\"2\">FAST-TEMPO TRAINING SHOES WITH HIGH PERFORMANCE TECHNOLOGY.</font></pre><p class=\"gl-vspace\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve-breaks;\">The Boston Marathon is a race. But it\'s also a goal, and a training plan and all the days it stays on your mind before the big one. The Adizero Boston 12 Shoes are built for mid- to long-distance running. They bring a race-day feel to training with a propulsive feel that comes from the glass-fibre infused ENERGYRODS 2.0, which limit energy loss underfoot. They\'re fast, but that does not come at the cost of durability — the midsole layers ultra-light LIGHTSTRIKE PRO cushioning with a new version of durable LIGHTSTRIKE 2.0 EVA.</p>', 'Adizero_Boston_12_Shoes_White_JQ2552_HM1.avif', 'Adizero_Boston_12_Shoes_White_JQ2552_HM3_hover.avif', 'Adizero_Boston_12_Shoes_White_JQ2552_HM4.avif', 0, 'In Stock', '2025-05-24 13:31:52', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(10, 4, 33, 'Supernova Rise 2 Running Shoes', 'Adidas', 12000, 15000, '<h3 class=\"subtitle___9ljbp\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: AdineuePRO, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 32px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space-collapse: preserve-breaks;\"><font size=\"2\">Supercomfort. Supernova.</font></h3><p class=\"gl-vspace\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: AdihausDIN, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve-breaks;\">You got into running, and now there\'s a race on your calendar. Keep making progress in these Adidas running shoes for daily runs. They ride on a Dreamstrike+ midsole, our lightweight super foam tuned for comfort. Support Rods help guide you from heel strike to toe off. Our new refined engineered sandwich mesh upper and premium heel construction is elegantly designed for optimized breathability for our most comfortable fit yet. Recognized by the American Podiatric Medical Association for promoting good foot health, this is Supernova Rise 2.</p>', 'Pureboost_5_Running_Shoes_Black_JH6445_02_standard.avif', 'Pureboost_5_Running_Shoes_Black_JH6445_01_00_standard.avif', 'Pureboost_5_Running_Shoes_Black_JH6445_03_standard.avif', 0, 'In Stock', '2025-05-24 13:34:20', NULL, NULL, NULL),
